{
  "texts": [
    "D Complete Main ExperimentsTo demonstrate the general applicability of our framework, we also apply our method to T5-large (Raffel et al., 2020).",
    "We provide the complete main experiment results in Table 4, including results on T5-large and on LLaMA-2-7B checkpoints.",
    "These new models are trained in the separate setting, which means they are trained on each individual dataset instead of the mixture.",
    "We also include additional baselines ICL LLaMA-2-13B and Self-RAG (Asai et al., 2023).",
    "Note that RL experiments for the separate training settings are run only once, since we observe little variation when repeating them with different seeds."
  ]
}